data.description: Discover this two-story home located in a cul-de-sac with 3 Bedrooms, a Bonus Room, and 2.5 Bathrooms. Enjoy the Sterling Farms community which has amenities such as the Clubhouse and Community Pool. This home recently had a makeover with many updates anda a fresh coat of paint, new flooring in most rooms and features a spacious family room with ceiling fan and fireplace.The new layout in the kitchen boasts plenty of cabinets for stoarge, custom tile backsplash and a pantry.  On the upper level, you'll find the Owners Suite with new flooring, a walk-in closet, a ceiling fan and a private bathroom with dual vanities, soaking tub and seperate walk in shower. Additionally, you will find 2 more Bedrooms along with the Bonus room which offers an additional seperate flex space that can easily be utilized as a home office, game room, or private sitting area. SELLER TO PROVIDE 1 YEAR 2/10 HOME WARRANTY! Call today to schedule your private tour.
